video.title: Distance - Sprint Tournament (August 2017)
video.description: On August 12th, 2017 we held Distance's first ever Sprint tournament! Over 50 competitors raced to take the crown, with the winner earning a special shirt and poster from Refract. Special thanks to Krispy and Splaysh for excellently organizing this event, and to PPPaul, Plasmawario, and Platoonsgt1 for creating incredible levels specifically for the tournament!
